| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6853 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 77df1c95-4446-5b10-8e7d-7519b53ad4c0"
